      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offered is a museum-grade 2004 BMW M3, featuring the legendary S54B32 power plant. This high-revving 3.2L inline-six utilizes individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing to deliver linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Power is managed through a precise Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and delivered to the rear wheels via a factory M-variable differential lock. The chassis remains structurally flawless with documented subframe reinforcement already completed. This example retains its original paint with factory-spec tolerances and zero oxidation. Mechanically sorted with a recent valve adjustment and rod bearing service, this E46 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated Bavarian engineering in pristine, collector-quality condition.",
